caption.text:
Ever pick up a used copy of 
Black, white, black 2 and white 2 and ever look at them like "Man i wish i could get the old event mons/items"

Well...what if i told you that In 2019 (2020) you can access them.

With 1 simple non game breaking/ bricking system exploit.

Called: the Dns server trick.
This can be preformed with a 3ds family system and can also work for the original ds family line (not dsi line) ------
Without further adu gen 5.
How to preform the trick:
Step one: Go into your Wi-Fi settings 
Step 2. Change the dns settings on your primary Wi-Fi connection
Only the primary settings and insert these numbers
164.132.44.106. 
Then hit okay and you're done!
----
You can preform this trick with gen 4 but it requires alot more effort that is difficult for me to explain so i have provided a link in my bio for how to do gen 4.
----
What mystery gifts can you get for gen 5? 
Well....the mythicals for that gen.
For black and white the liberty ticket to get victini
Bw2 to get genesect
Every single gen 5 Wi-Fi event is available 
Even the Japanese, or other country events
Note: the events are randomized and some will duplicate so its a gamble to get them all
If you have missed any events, or wanted to relive nostalgia then this is the trick for you!
These events can be transfered up to gen 7 through pokebank.

Also note for gen 4: if you get the Arceus, Shaymin and darkrai event they can be soft reset to get shiny 
This also works for pokemon ranger shadow of almia and guardian signs to get the manaphy egg event mission
------

Recuerdan que hace una semana le regalé a mi esposa el super mario party? Esta semana me tocó a mí el regalo. Uno de los mejores regalos que me han podido hacer en tods mi vids es este. Años que no jugaba este zelda, y como dato extra nunca lo había tenido en físico (el videojuego no lo llegué a jugar en la game boy, fue en un emulador). Sinceramente de los zeldas que más cariño le tengo y que, a pesar de su sencillez, pienso que es un juego muy completo y que le da mil vueltas a cualquier otro zelda para una portátil. Con un apartado artístico adorable, pienso que, si conoces a alguien y quieres que se adentre en esta saga, este me parece de las mejores opciones para que lo haga. Amé este juego.

caption.text:
Among the see of yellow and turquoise Switch Lite out there, can we have some love for the grey ones too? 
___
I will keep this short and honest but as of right now if you own an OG Switch, this is an luxury item, it is a want not a need. Don't rush in buying a Lite, if you have extra cash saved up, then go for it! .
Now, personally, I love this little thing! I now wish that the OG Switch came out in this form and size. I'm also seriously considering if I need a grip for this, the size is perfect for my hands! I've played two hours straight, and I felt no cramps or stress on my hands. .
If you're like me and enjoy taking a handheld console with you at work or anywhere, the Switch Lite is a perfect companion for you. I'll probably regret this later if I don't get a grip for the Lite, but I can honestly say this is most comfortable handheld system I ever played with! 
___
So, if you bought a Switch Lite, what colour did you go for? If you're thinking of getting one, what colour would you get?

caption.text: La Consola Perfecta No Exis... #nintendoswitch  #homebrew  #pumpitup #musicgames

Naughty Dog dijo que aquellos que no hayan actualizado sus consolas aún podrán obtener una experiencia completa. La plataforma objetivo para el juego es la PS4 base, según el desarrollador, por lo que aquellos que se han resistido a la actualización todavía pueden esperar el juego.
____ «Nuestra plataforma objetivo es la PS4, la base«, dijo Schatz, a USgamer. «Eso es en realidad lo que tengo en mi escritorio en el trabajo, y eso es a lo que apuntamos«. Schatz reconoció las ventajas de PlayStation 4 Pro y dijo que aún queda mucho trabajo por hacer para lograr velocidades de fotogramas y resoluciones específicas, entre otros objetivos. «Así que sí, quieres tener ese equilibrio, pero ya sabes, todavía hay mucha optimización por hacer«, dijo . «Lo que viste aquí no es nuestra velocidad de cuadro final y resolución de pantalla final, cosas así«.
____

Pemimpin dalam pengembangan dan penerbitan game Gameloft, mengumumkan bahwa Asphalt 9: Legends, entri terbaru dalam waralaba balap mobil yang paling banyak diunduh, dan mendapatkan multi-penghargaan di dunia, akhirnya tersedia untuk pre-order untuk Nintendo Switch ™ di Nintendo eShop. Asphalt 9: Legends akan diluncurkan di seluruh dunia sebagai game gratis untuk diunduh pada 8 Oktober 2019.

Here’s my Mario Maker 2 Switch Design! Here’s basically the design choices I made:
.
The Mario Maker 2 background has a grid, and so I decided that with this “construction” theme I could make it easier to read the name, with a solid color at the bottom. I think it turned out pretty nicely.
.
Yellow and red joycons along with the steel book are all pretty standard for most switch bundles
.
The Mario pipe just seemed to fit well and really being in the feeling of a “Mario game”. I think that I’ll add the hand with the pencil on it to make it more of a Mario maker image.
.
A bit of an error by me- there’s a steel book but it says full game download so...
.
That’’s basically it! If there are any designs you’d like me to make lmk in the comments!
.

Dragon Quest XI

Dragon Quest XI: Echoes of an Elusive Age is a role-playing video game developed and published by Square Enix. An entry in the long-running Dragon Quest video game series, it was released in Japan for the Nintendo 3DS and PlayStation 4 in July 2017, and worldwide for the PlayStation 4 and Microsoft Windows in September 2018. An enhanced version for the Nintendo Switch, titled Dragon Quest XI S: Echoes of an Elusive Age - Definitive Edition, was released in September 2019.
